  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌙 <strong><i>Harvest Corrupted Souls, Restore the Lost Stars, and Bring Salvation to a Broken World.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/622d85fab80eac77fbb9631a4c3dc21b.avif?t=1757056269\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras_big/622d85fab80eac77fbb9631a4c3dc21b.webp?t=1757056269 width=1560 height=505 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The stars that once sealed away ancient evils have fallen and shattered, unleashing the long-imprisoned darkness. It awakens sorrow long forgotten and stirs desires left behind, spreading its corruption across the world. As a novice Reaper, your vital first harvest begins now. The mission is simple and clear: claim the corrupted souls, restore light to the lost stars, and let them once again illuminate the sky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/a2bf1b384bf9f1c53e0bd65cc55241c4.webp?t=1757056269\" width=1560 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Moonlit Reaper</i>, every stage is a desperate fight for survival. Cut down swarms of enemies with a diverse arsenal of weapons and ancient abilities, and hold the line through fast-paced hack-and-slash combat mixed with strategic base defense. As you endure relentless waves of corruption, harvest their souls, unlock lost constellations, and transcend every defeat, forging a path to restore a broken world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/9cd9d1c4b2c403ead52861ee789cb91a.poster.avif?t=1757056269\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/9cd9d1c4b2c403ead52861ee789cb91a.webm?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/9cd9d1c4b2c403ead52861ee789cb91a.mp4?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⭐ Restore All Constellations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Rebuild the fallen stars one by one. Complete constellations and receive their powerful, cosmic blessings.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/1e9b1c12443ae049384ea0022147466d.poster.avif?t=1757056269\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/1e9b1c12443ae049384ea0022147466d.webm?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/1e9b1c12443ae049384ea0022147466d.mp4?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🕯️ Harvest and Purify Souls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Hunt down corrupted souls and purify them. Transform their power into your own and grow stronger than ever before.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/97b864a791cf95aee9576f1a22e3ac73.poster.avif?t=1757056269\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/97b864a791cf95aee9576f1a22e3ac73.webm?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/97b864a791cf95aee9576f1a22e3ac73.mp4?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚔️ Collect and Forge Your Arsenal</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Gather and wield up to 8 harvesters at once. Master powerful combinations to dominate the battlefield.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/ee7d18d70a84d1ac5d6cb9c05145c5fb.poster.avif?t=1757056269\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/ee7d18d70a84d1ac5d6cb9c05145c5fb.webm?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/ee7d18d70a84d1ac5d6cb9c05145c5fb.mp4?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔮 Protect World Purity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Enemies that escape the battlefield spread corruption. Let none escape and keep the world pure.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/06b44853347bfa951914fc368c8f9234.poster.avif?t=1757056269\" width=1170 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/06b44853347bfa951914fc368c8f9234.webm?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/06b44853347bfa951914fc368c8f9234.mp4?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌀 Embrace Transcendence</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Sometimes, retreat is the wisest path. Embrace defeat to transcend your limits and prepare for an even greater leap forward.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/a92e6e95694251b1a54b7918f620f95f.poster.avif?t=1757056269\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/a92e6e95694251b1a54b7918f620f95f.webm?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634700/extras/a92e6e95694251b1a54b7918f620f95f.mp4?t=1757056269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
